      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<blockquote>根据马克思韦伯的”除魅”理论<br/>\n<br/>\n独裁者的光环被笑话幽默渐渐消蚀,人们也就不再敬畏和恐惧政权</blockquote><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/50351\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/50351\">为什么中共领袖缺乏幽默感？</a> </div>",
      "date": "2022-12-12",
